note over browser:
User hits submit button
end note

note over browser:
new note is appended to HTML list of elements
end note

note over browser:
new note is sent to server as JSON string
end note

browser->server: HTTP POST https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/new_note_spa
browser-->server: JSON: [{ date: "2021-12-30T08:51:20.861Z", content: "new note" }]

note over server:
Server processes form data, 
adds new note to database, 
end note
